so on.
This is obvious for every one not you,me or anyone, for every lives, for every state of energy realize affinity towards higher state of energy for their stability.

But this affinity is also the base of attachment/making the bound/stress/happy/sad/complexity/solution/problem..etc.

How it is possible? The base/seed is a natural affinity and the tree build on that become ugly?
